{"tid":2000144,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"廣告迷思","createTime":"2020-05-03T15:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T15:55:35.000Z","uid":306198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"530b3cf63a0bc741a18666c0951652e975e89946","tid":2000144,"uid":306198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"點解一個黃嘅YouTuber 同中資賣廣告要俾人鬧？<br />\n<br />\n富途牛牛真心好用 連大J同COCO哥都推介<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1989270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1989270</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n假設佢哋嘅觀眾大部分喺黃，如果佢哋一賣完廣告就令大部分黃嘅人用富途嘅話。<br />\n<br />\n咁大規模嘅黃店例如759係咪應該要搵藍嘅youtuber去賣廣告，令多啲對家支持黃店？<br />\n<br />\n咁係呢個情況，我諗759應該又會俾人因為資助對家又俾人話偽黃。<br />\n<br />\n純粹想討論吓，並非引戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}